# Copy to .dev.vars for local dev (never commit .dev.vars).
# All optional. The "Should I Loop?" tool runs on its heuristic without any key.

# Option A: OpenAI-hosted refinement
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Option B: Anthropic-hosted refinement
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-3-5-haiku-latest

# Option C: Cloudflare Workers AI (enable the "ai" binding in wrangler.jsonc instead)
